      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<div class=\"article-content\">\n<section class=\"article-body\">\n<h3 id=\"h_01HXYS9SF6KY1EAQ17VRHQQAWX\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5rem 0px; font-family: ' Source Sans Pro' , ' Source Serif Pro' , -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, ' Segoe UI' , Roboto, ' Helvetica Neue' , Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.5; color: #2a303e; font-size: 1rem; text-transform: uppercase; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Added</h3>\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #2a303e; font-family: ' Source Sans Pro' , ' Source Serif Pro' , -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, ' Segoe UI' , Roboto, ' Helvetica Neue' , Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n<a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-41298\">​</a><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-41364\">LCD-41364</a><span> </span>- Cookie Preference Management:</strong><span> Added a new tab on the Preferences page that allows users to manage their cookie consent preferences. <br></span>\n</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n<strong><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-41645\">LCD-41645</a></strong><span><strong> - View Certificate Expiration Date:</strong> The expiration dates of certificates are now listed on the Certificates page with indicators to inform users of expired certificates and certificates that are about to expire.</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"h_01HXYS9NRE5H6PTZ9Y99PF8QQH\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5rem 0px; font-family: ' Source Sans Pro' , ' Source Serif Pro' , -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, ' Segoe UI' , Roboto, ' Helvetica Neue' , Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.5; color: #2a303e; font-size: 1rem; text-transform: uppercase; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Bug Fixes</h3>\n<ul class=\"ak-ul\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #2a303e; font-family: ' Source Sans Pro' , ' Source Serif Pro' , -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, ' Segoe UI' , Roboto, ' Helvetica Neue' , Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-43023\">LCD-43023</a> - OpenVPN Setup Bug: </strong>Fixed an issue where certain OpenVPN setups would fail to connect.</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>"
      },
